1. *Pitamo* se ko će biti novi predsednik. (We wonder who will be the new president.)
2. Da li *pitamo* roditelje za dozvolu? (Should we ask our parents for permission?)
3. Želim da *pitam* direktora nekoliko pitanja. (I want to ask the director a few questions.)
4. Nisam siguran da li će mi *pitati* adresu. (I'm not sure if they will ask me for the address.)
5. Kad god *pitate* nešto, budite ljubazni. (Whenever you ask something, be polite.)
6. Moramo *pitati* za cenu pre nego što kupimo auto. (We have to ask for the price before we buy the car.)
7. Oni obično *pitaju* isto pitanje svaki dan. (They usually ask the same question every day.)
8. Da li ćete *pitati* profesora o zadatku? (Will you ask the professor about the assignment?)
9. Ko će *pitati* na sastanku sutra? (Who will ask questions at the meeting tomorrow?)
10. Molim vas da *pitajte* pre nego što donesete odluku. (Please ask before you make a decision.)